B-NE ABEE TAALIB WAL-ITA-MAAME BAALE MOHAMMADIN HANEE-FAN MUSLEMAN WA MAA ANAA MINAL MUSHRE-KEENA.", "ArabicText1": "عَلٰی مِلَّۃِ اِبْرَاهِیْمَ وَدِیْنَ مَحَمَّدٍ وَّمَنْهَاجِ عَلِیِّ بْنِ اَبِیْ طَالِبْ وَالْاِتَمَامِ بَآلِ مُحَمَّدٍ حَنِیْفًا مُسْلِمًا وَمَا اَنَا مِنَ الْمُشْرِكِیْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1016774, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "Imam Mahdi (a) wrote in reply to Humairi that: Paying attention to this supplication is not compulsory but the recommended precaution regarding it, which is also in accordance to the consensus of all the clerics, is the following…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Imam Mahdi (a) ne jawab-e-tehreer farmaya; Is dua ka namaz ke shuru mein padhna waajib nahi hai bal-keh mustahab-e-mokad (taakeed ki gayi) hai is tarah kaho…", "UrduDescription": "حضرت امام زمانہؑ نے جواب میں فرمایا نماز کے آغاز میں دعا کا پڑھنا واجب نہیں ہے بلکہ مستحب موکد ہے اس جھت سے کہ اجماع کے مانند ہے اس میں کوئی اختلاف نہیں ہے اور نماز کے آغاز میں یوں لکھو۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1002695, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "I have directed my face towards the one who created the Heavens and the Earth while I am a worshipper who surrenders before Him, I have faith upon the nation of Ibrahim and the religion of Mohammad and the guidance of the Commander of the faithful, indeed my prayer, my rites of sacrifice, my living and my death are for Allah, the Lord of the worlds. No partner has He, and this I have been commanded, and I am the first (among You) of the Muslims. O Allah, regard me among the Muslims, I seek refuge in Allah, the Hearer, the Knower, from Satan, the expelled, in the name of Allah, the Beneficent, the Merciful.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Mai ne apna rukh us Khuda ki taraf kiya jo aasmaano aur zameen ka khaaliq, ghaayab o haazir ka jaanne waala hai, baatil se kata huwa farman-bardaar hu, aur mushriko’n se nahi hu, be-shak meri namaz meri ibaadat aur meri zindagi aur meri maut Khuda ke liye hai jo jahano ka Rab hai, Uska koi saani nahi mujhe yahi hukm mila aur mai farmaan-bardaaro’n mein se hu.", "Urdu": "میں نے اپنا رُخ اس خدا کی طرف کیا جو آسمانوں اور زمین کا خالق غائب و حاضر کا جاننے والا ہے باطل سے کٹا ہوا فرما بردار ہوں اورمشرکوں سے نہیں ہوں بے شک میری نماز میری عبادت اور میری زندگی اور میری موت خدا کےلیے ہے جو جہانوں کا رب ہے اس کا کوئی ثانی نہیں مجھے یہی حکم ملا اور میں فرماں برداروں میں سے ہوں۔", "RArabic": "WAJJAH-TO WAJHE-YA LIL-LAZEE FATA-RIS SAMAA-WAATE WAL-ARZA HANEE-FAN MUSLE-MAN A’LAA MILLATE IBRAAHEEMA WA DEENE MOHAMMADIN WA HODA AMEERIL MOMENEENA WA MAA ANAA MINAL MUSHRE-KEEN, INNA SALAA-TEE WA NOSO-KEE WA MAH-YAAYA WA MAMAA-TEE LILLAAHE RABBIL A’ALA-MEENA, LAA SHAREEKA LAHU WA BE-ZAALEKA O-MIRTO ANAA MINAL MUSLE-MEENA. ALLAAHUM-MAJ A’LNEE MINAL MUSLE-MEENA, AOO’ZO BILLAA-HIS SAMEE-I’L A’LEEME ME-NASH SHAIYTAA-NIR RAJEEME, BISMILLAA-HIR RAHMAA-NIR RAHEEME, SUMMA TAQARAL HAMDIN.", "ArabicText1": "وَجَّهْتُ وَجْهِیَ لِلَّذِیْ فَطَرِ السَّمَاوَتِ وَالْاَرْضَ حَنِیْفًا مُسْلِمًا عَلٰی مِلَّۃِ اِبْرَاهِیْمَ وَدِیْنِ مُحَمَّدٍ وَهُدٰی اَمِیْرِ الْمُؤْمِنِیْنَ وَمَا اَنَا مِنَ الْمُشْرِكِیْنَ، اِنَّ صَلَاتِیْ وَنُسُكِیْ وَمَحْیَایَ وَمَمَاتِیْ لِلهِ رَبِّ الْعَالَمِیْنَ، لَا شَرِیْكَ لَهٗ وَبِذٰلِكَ اُمِرْتُ اَنَا مِنَ الْمُسْلِمِیْنَ۔ اَللّٰھُمَّ اجْعَلْنِیْ مِنَ الْمُسْلِمِیْنَ، اَعُوْذُ بِاللهِ السَّمِیْعِ الْعَلِیْمِ مِنَ الشَّیْطَانِ الرَّجِیْمِ، بِسْمِ اللهِ الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِیْمِ ثُمَّ تَقَرًا الْحَمْدٍ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduI